                        <h3><a href="#">Bibliographic Source(s)</a></h3>
                    <p><table><tr><td>Rubin LG, Levin MJ, Ljungman P, Davies EG, Avery R, Tomblyn M, Bousvaros A, Dhanireddy S, Sung L, Keyserling H, Kang I. 2013 IDSA clinical practice guideline for vaccination of the immunocompromised host. Clin Infect Dis. 2014 Feb;58(3):e44-e100. [484 references] <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180712204847/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=24311479" target="_blank">PubMed</a> <img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712204847im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></td></tr></table></p>
