                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>The guidelines for vaccination of hematopoietic stem cell transplant (HSCT) candidates and recipients have been adapted from the following source: Tomblyn M, Chiller T, Einsele H, et al. Guidelines for preventing infectious complications among hematopoietic cell transplantation recipients: a global perspective. Biol Blood Marrow Transplant 2009; 15:1143&ndash;238.</p></div></p>
